# Coroot CE Lab on OpenShift 4.18

Validated lab for Coroot CE on OpenShift 4.18.x using Coroot Operator and a pinned custom node-agent.

## Validated Environment

- OpenShift: 4.18.38
- Coroot Operator Helm Chart: coroot-operator-0.9.4
- Coroot Operator App Version: 1.9.3
- Custom Node Agent: ghcr.io/coroot/coroot-node-agent:1.28.3

## Known Issue

The node-agent deployed by the Coroot Operator may fail on OCP 4.18 due to eBPF/verifier incompatibility.

Workaround:

1. Install Coroot Operator
2. Create Coroot CR
3. Disable operator-managed node-agent
4. Deploy custom node-agent `1.28.3`

## Install Coroot Operator

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/00-namespace.yaml

helm repo add coroot https://coroot.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update

helm install coroot-operator coroot/coroot-operator -n coroot

Create Coroot Instance
oc apply -f coroot/01-coroot-cr.yaml
oc get pods -n coroot -w
Disable Operator Node Agent
oc patch ds coroot-node-agent -n coroot --type=merge --patch-file coroot/02-disable-operator-node-agent-patch.yaml
Deploy Custom Node Agent
oc adm policy add-scc-to-user privileged -z coroot-node-agent-custom -n coroot
oc apply -f coroot/03-node-agent-custom.yaml
Validate
oc get pods -n coroot
oc logs -n coroot -l app.kubernetes.io/component=coroot-node-agent-custom --tail=30

Expected:

metrics remote write endpoint: http://coroot-coroot.coroot:8080/v1/metrics
sent metrics in XXms

